nodes.text: Flimsicard was a substance used to make items such as boxes to hold food. The dining establishment Sakhet's Noodles used flimsicard boxes to give food, such as Corellian buckwheat noodles or nerf nuggets, to their customers. In 0 ABY, Luke Skywalker and Nakari Kelen received food from Sakhet's Noodles in flimsicard boxes.
